description: Sonic's previous owners have come to take him away and they refuse to take no for an answer. Could this be the end of the Sonic Underground as we know it...?
fulltitle: Sonic's Adoption Parents Come To Take Him Away

comments.text:
Sonic’s adoptive parents raised Sonic after Queen Aleena gave up her children and separated them to different families due to Robotnik’s takeover of Mobius. Manic was raised by a thief, and Sonia was raised by an aristocrat. Sonic later revved to Uncle Chuck due to Robotnik’s forces arresting Sonic’s foster parents, presumably to be roboticized.

After Robotnik’s forces found out about the adoptive parents and Chuck’s connections to the triplets, the parents and Chuck were captured by Robotnik’s forces, and roboticized.
